@startuml
' @id(SEQ-MAP-SCOPE)
' @ref(USE-SCOPED-REMAP)
' @desc(SEQ-MAP-SCOPE, "Project::map_scope(N) builds DOM-MAP-SCOPE-PLAN. Read the cycle N manifest (touched_files, scope). REVERSE (touched_files): for each touched file, scan trace.yml source_links for entries whose path matches (reuse CMP-TRACE-ENGINE path matching); collect their model_id @ids; map each current-side @id to the current diagram file declaring it; add to affected_files. A touched file matching no source_link is pushed to scope_escapes. FORWARD (scope): for each objective scope @id, add the current-side concept file <kind>/<name> that realizes it to affected_files. full_remap = scope_escapes non-empty. The /mdd-cycle loop runs the verb each iteration and hands affected_files (or 'whole tree' on full_remap) to /mdd-map; /mdd-validate then runs whole-tree regardless.")
' Objective sequence realizing USE-SCOPED-REMAP (cycle 0030). The same
' source_link inversion that backs SEQ-MAP-STATUS, turned around to emit
' a cheaper re-map plan rather than a freshness verdict.
title Scoped re-map — map-scope plan (objective)

participant "/mdd-cycle loop\n(CMP-CYCLE-ORCHESTRATOR)" as Cycle
participant "mdd map-scope\n(CMP-MAP-SCOPE-CLI)" as Cli
participant "Project::map_scope()\n(CMP-MAP-SCOPE-ENGINE)" as Engine
participant "CycleRegistry\nmanifest" as Manifest
participant "trace.yml\nsource_links" as Trace
participant "path matcher\n(CMP-TRACE-ENGINE)" as Matcher
participant "MapScopePlan" as Plan
participant "/mdd-map" as Map

Cycle -> Cli : map-scope --cycle N --json
Cli -> Engine : map_scope(N)
Engine -> Manifest : read cycle N (touched_files, scope)
Manifest --> Engine : touched_files, scope

== Reverse (touched_files since last iteration) ==
loop each touched file
  Engine -> Trace : source_links with matching path
  Trace --> Engine : (model_id, path)*
  alt at least one source_link matches
    Engine -> Matcher : path match
    Matcher --> Engine : model_ids
    Engine -> Plan : add current diagram file(s) for those @ids
  else no source_link
    Engine -> Plan : push scope_escape (forces full_remap)
  end
end

== Forward (objective scope @ids) ==
loop each scope @id in manifest
  Engine -> Plan : add current-side concept file realizing it
end

Plan --> Engine : { cycle, affected_files, scope_escapes, full_remap }
Engine --> Cli : DOM-MAP-SCOPE-PLAN
Cli --> Cycle : JSON plan

alt full_remap
  Cycle -> Map : re-derive whole current/ tree
else narrowed
  Cycle -> Map : re-derive only affected_files (rest byte-identical)
end
@enduml
